              <p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/pages/industries/fmcg.astro:txt-1">Time-bound safety notices and recall messaging that can be applied at the right level of granularity — product, variant, or batch strategy — presented clearly at the top of the passport when it matters.</p>
